(Final Summary):  This is an NTR manga.  MC was NTR'ed (only in text), and now he is in the process of Netori-ing FMC, and Netori-ing FMC's mom. FMC's mom is also in a way NTRing her daughter who may be developing feelings for MC again.

(Crappy Translation p3): MC proceeds to fuck FMC's brains out, and clearly impresses him to the point where she thinks he's found a boyfriend.  MC asks he is better than FMC's boyfriend, and she clearly thinks he is, but is too embarrassed to admit it and says that MC is no where close but if he insists, she will think about it (but MC just runs off after hearing that [p52]).  MC goes back to the mom telling her that he failed, so she agrees to keep practicing with him until he steals FMC away from her boyfriend.

(Crappy Translation p2): FMC's mom overhears all of this, and since she prefers the MC to date her daughter and decides to training arc him to help him steal FMC from her BF.  During training arc, he ends up liking FMC's mom more and more as they fuck a lot.

Finally the day has come and FMC's mom points him in FMC's direction, MC wants to "confess" to FMC's mom, but she cuts of him and he does the deed.

(Crappy Translation p1): 

MC had a boyish childhood friend that he liked who actually liked him back, but she thought MC only saw her as a boy, so she consulted with a friend on what to (become more feminine), but ended up getting taken. (She confesses that to him in her room, but he doesn't talk about his own feelings)

FMC decides to cheat on her current bf to pop MC's cherry, and after the deed MC asks her to break up with her BF and date him instead, but she turns him down saying that it's too late, but if MC is better at sex than her BF, she will consider it, but for now, they can only be sex friends.
